        "timestamp": "2021-04-20 08:15:03.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi, Please review and approve if everything OK. Just some info - The number of files committed are very big in number but please be aware that it is just a reorganization of the directory structure of the devicemanagers and nothing else. The base devicemanager which was till now in the \"devicemanager\" directory is now renamed as \"devicemanager-core\". 2 new directories - devicemanager-onap and devicemanager-o-ran-sc were created and the specific devicemanagers are moved to those new directories.\n\nRegards,\nRavi",
        "patchset_number": 2
